---
title: Indian Inspired Vegetable Pilaf with Mango Chutney, Yoghurt and Flaked Almonds
description: Our Indian Inspired Vegetable Pilaf with Mango Chutney, Yoghurt and Flaked Almonds is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220824_R20_W40_UK_V12126-5_KB_Main_low-baa1a1b0.jpg
